CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1963, pg. 1, reads: "Will Demonstrations Be Staged Here? - Members of Pittsburgh's newly formed Unity Committee have selected several targets around Pittsburgh as sites of possible mass demonstrations.
